<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:geo="http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#" xmlns:georss="http://www.georss.org/georss" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/"><channel><title>广告牌</title><atom:link href="https://www.billboard.com/feed/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><link/> https://www.billboard.com<description>音乐排行榜、新闻、照片和视频</description><lastbuilddate>2024 年 7 月 1 日星期一 02:26:00 +0000</lastbuilddate><language> en-US</language><sy:updateperiod>每小时</sy:updateperiod><sy:updatefrequency>1</sy:updatefrequency><generator> https://wordpress.org/?v=6.4.5</generator><site xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 200641670</site><item><title>泰勒·斯威夫特在都柏林演出《有史以来最小的人》中遇到舞台故障</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/taylor-swift-stage-malfunction-smallest-man-who-ever-lived-dublin-1235721189/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ashley Iasimone]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 01 Jul 2024 02:25:51 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music News]]></category><category><![CDATA[Concerts]]></category><category><![CDATA[News]]></category><category><![CDATA[Pop]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235721189 </guid><description><![CDATA[Swift didn't flinch over the glitch at Saturday night's Eras concert.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>周六在都柏林举行的“有史以来最小的人”演出开始时<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/taylor-swift/"  >，泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的舞台没有按计划进行。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>这位流行偶像在<em>《The Tortured Poets Department》</em>歌曲的前几行中说道：“这是真的吗/满怀幻想地看着我/穿着你的耶和华见证人套装/那家伙到底是谁？” — 音乐会观众注意到舞台出现故障。斯威夫特所站的高架部分未能按预期下降，让她暂时陷入困境。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/taylor-swift-eras-tour-dublin-june-28-2024-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 Eras 巡演都柏林" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在混搭现场首次亮相“The Albatross”，并演唱了一首“Reputation”歌曲…… </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024年6月29日</time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>斯威夫特并没有因为这个故障而退缩。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>幸运的是，她没等太久，一位舞者扬·拉夫尼克就伸出援助之手，把她扶了下来。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>在<a  rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"  href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C82V1FkSsqW/?hl=en"  target="_blank"  >一位粉丝发布的</a>斯威夫特<em>《折磨诗人》</em>音乐会的特写视频中，在拉夫尼克提供帮助时，这位流行歌星看起来和听起来都在努力忍住笑声。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>演出必须继续下去，斯威夫特的三个半小时的演出做到了。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>斯威夫特的国际 Eras 巡演本周末在都柏林英杰华体育场举行了三场音乐会。接下来，她将于 7 月 4 日至 6 日前往阿姆斯特丹，在 Johan Cruijff Arena 进行三场约会。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>周日， <em>《公告牌》</em>宣布斯威夫特的<em>《The Tortured Poets Department》</em>连续第 10 周在公告牌 200 专辑排行榜上<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-10th-week-number-one-billboard-200-chart-1235720993/"  >排名第一</a>。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>至此，斯威夫特已经在 The Eras Tour 巡演中现场演奏了至少一次 31 首曲目中的大部分曲目。该节目的<em>“折磨诗人”</em>部分包括歌曲“但爸爸我爱他”，有点像“So High School”，“谁害怕小老我？”和“Down Bad”，过渡到“Fortnight”。它以“有史以来最小的人”（通常有一个正常运行的舞台）和“我可以带着破碎的心做到这一点”结束。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/taylor-swift-stevie-nicks-2010-grammys-duet-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 史蒂夫·尼克斯" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在史蒂夫·尼克斯 (Stevie Nicks) 面前演奏《克拉拉·弓》(Clara Bow)，以现场首演《折磨诗人》曲目…… </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024/06/30 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>专辑中的其他曲目已在斯威夫特的原声部分首次现场亮相，其中她提供了两首令人惊喜的歌曲表演。本周末的首秀包括<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/taylor-swift-the-albatross-live-dancing-with-our-hands-tied-dublin-1235720897/"  >周六的“The Albatross”</a>和<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/taylor-swift-stevie-nicks-clara-bow-eras-tour-dublin-1235721023/"  >周日的“Clara Bow”</a> ，Stevie Nicks 则在 VIP 帐篷里用手机拍摄了斯威夫特的歌曲。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>请参阅下面的斯威夫特熟练处理周六舞台故障的片段。 </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">仔细观察昨晚在都柏林举行的“有史以来最小的人”期间的舞台故障<a  href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TaylorSwift?src=hash&#038;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >#TaylorSwift</a> <a  href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DublinTSTheErasTour?src=hash&#038;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >#DublinTSTheErasTour</a> <a  href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/TSTheErasTour?src=hash&#038;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >#TSTheErasTour</a> <a  href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/taylorsversion?src=hash&#038;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >#taylorsversion</a> <a  href="https://t.co/2OkQntR6dN"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >pic.twitter.com/2OkQntR6dN</a></p> - Swiftie&#39;s Unite (@swiftiesaunite) <a  href="https://twitter.com/swiftiesaunite/status/1807553461812146481?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="es" dir="ltr"> 🚨|今天，在都柏林举行的 The Eras Tour 的第二场演出中，大家都看到了法雅斯技术和潘塔拉斯场景。 <a  href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DublinTSTheErasTour?src=hash&#038;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >#DublinTSTheErasTour</a> <a  href="https://t.co/AUBmGgGtYm"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >pic.twitter.com/AUBmGgGtYm</a></p> - 泰勒访问 (@TheTaylorAccess) <a  href="https://twitter.com/TheTaylorAccess/status/1807487666847437270?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"  rel="nofollow"  target="_blank"  >2024 年 6 月 30 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235721189</post-id></item><item><title> 2024 年 BET 大奖：演出最佳照片</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/photos/bet-awards-2024-best-photos-1235721303/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jenny Regan]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 01 Jul 2024 02:13:56 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[R&B/Hip-Hop]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc-gallery&amp;p=1235721303</guid><description><![CDATA[Will Smith, Tyla, Sexyy Red and more.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p> 2024 年 BET 颁奖典礼于周日（6 月 30 日）晚上在洛杉矶孔雀剧院举行。第三次由塔拉吉·P·汉森 (Taraji P. Henson) 主持，这位奥斯卡金像奖提名演员在梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 的歌曲混合表演后，模仿肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的公告牌百强单曲榜冠军歌曲《Not Like Us》，为节目开场。新专辑<em>《Megan</em> 》于周五发行。</p><p>威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith)、Sexyy Red、Tyla、Shaboozey（J-Kwon 也加入了！）、维多利亚·莫奈 (Victoria Monet)、Latto、GloRilla 等众多表演者齐聚一堂，亚瑟小子 (Usher) 在 2024 年 BET 颁奖典礼上获得了终身成就奖。史密斯表演了他的新歌“You Can Make It”的戏剧版本，其中包括周五和周日服务合唱。但在周日的 BET 颁奖典礼上，史密斯与钱德勒·摩尔、柯克·富兰克林和周日服务合唱团一起发表了这首歌。</p><p>在节目中，汉森暂时停止了模仿歌曲、小品和妙语连珠的表演，发表了热情洋溢的演讲，恳求观众在 11 月份的总统选举中投票。 “这是一个严肃的时刻。这不仅仅是总统选举，”汉森说。 “你知道现在无家可归是犯罪吗？注意。他们正在攻击我们最脆弱的公民。 Project 2025 计划不是游戏。查一下。他们正试图恢复选秀。你觉得他们会先选谁呢？！我并不是想吓唬我们——我只是想告诉我们。我们有三个最高法院席位，你们——我们需要这些席位，否则我们就没有保护。”</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235721303</post-id></item><item><title>威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith) 与钱德勒·摩尔 (Chandler Moore)、柯克·富兰克林 (Kirk Franklin) 和周日服务合唱团 (Sunday Service Choir) 在 2024 年 BET 颁奖典礼上首次亮相“You Can Make It”</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/will-smith-you-can-make-it-2024-bet-awards-1235721159/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Heran Mamo]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 01 Jul 2024 02:00:14 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[bet awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music News]]></category><category><![CDATA[R&B/Hip-Hop]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235721159 </guid><description><![CDATA[The musician-actor released the song with Fridayy and Sunday Service Choir on June 28. ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>周日晚上（6 月 30 日），<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/will-smith/"  >威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith)</a>在 2024 年 BET 颁奖典礼上首次与钱德勒·摩尔 (Chandler Moore)、柯克·富兰克林 (Kirk Franklin) 和周日服务合唱团 (Sunday Service Choir) 一起表演了他的新单曲《You Can Make It》。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Usher-03-award-bet-awards-show-2024-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="招待员" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> 2024 年 BET 奖获奖者：查看完整列表（更新中） </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024/06/30 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “你在烟雾和火焰中/电线上的绳子很紧/我看到你已经破碎和疲惫/你所有的希望都破灭了/你刚刚受够了改变、游戏和耻辱/还有这个世界太疯狂了，所有的痛苦都来自火焰。”史密斯站在火圈中说道。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>但周日服务合唱团舒缓的和声和摩尔甜美的旋律使这首歌最初的压抑情绪发生了翻天覆地的变化。 “不要放弃我，我需要你坚持住/知道你深陷风暴/但我知道你可以面对它（面对它），哎/路上可能会变黑，而你” “我感觉很孤独/不要忘记你要去的地方/因为我知道你能成功，哦，哇，”摩尔在一场暴风雨扑灭大火并倾泻到史密斯身上之前唱道。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “哟，威尔，我可以作证吗？” <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/kirk-franklin/"  >“柯克·富兰克林</a>在上前布道时问道，要靠着上帝的恩典坚持度过艰难时期，而史密斯和周日礼拜合唱团则在红色舞台中央列队。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “没有人能一帆风顺/我们都有一个十字架要背负/但那火焰中蕴藏着智慧/你生命中的每一刻都是一个机会/我们没有受到惩罚，我们正在被锻造/在你的黑暗时刻跳舞，”史密斯在表演结束时郑重地说，“在你最黑暗的时刻跳舞”的字样在屏幕上方闪烁。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> “这是一种祝福，这是费城的传奇。我从小到大都是看着他长大的。我在 2020 年录制了那个 hook，然后将其发送给 Ayo，然后我认为 Ayo 今年开始与 Will 合作，并为他演奏了那个 hook。他就跳到了诗句上。所以这是一种祝福。”周五晚上早些时候，星期五在红地毯上<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/video/fridayy-talks-baddest-in-the-room-collaborating-with-will-smith-on-you-can-make-it-bet-awards-2024/"  >对<em>公告牌</em>R&amp;B/嘻哈音乐副总监卡尔·拉马尔 (Carl Lamarre) 说道</a>。 “我在私信中与他交谈过几次，但这是我第一次见到他。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>塔拉吉·P·汉森 (Taraji P. Henson) 第三次主持该节目。 2024 年 BET 奖在洛杉矶孔雀剧院举行。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>观看威尔·史密斯的首演“You Can Make It”如下： </p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy" class="youtube-player" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OhDgNoqkTrw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent" allowfullscreen="true" style="border:0;" sandbox="allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox"></iframe></div></figure></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235721159</post-id></item><item><title>性感红色电臀舞在 2024 年 BET 颁奖典礼上在白宫前“性感起来”</title><link/> https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/sexyy-red-get-it-sexyy-u-my-everything-2024-bet-awards-1235721235/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Angel Diaz]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 01 Jul 2024 01:53:15 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[bet awards]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music News]]></category><category><![CDATA[R&B/Hip-Hop]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?p=1235721235 </guid><description><![CDATA[The St. Louis rapper turned out a performance that had the crowd going wild.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-paywall"><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>圣路易斯的<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/sexyy-red/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/artist/sexyy-red/"  >性感红 (Sexyy Red)</a>周日（6 月 30 日）在洛杉矶孔雀剧院的表演为 2024 年 BET 颁奖典礼画上了圆满的句号。性感的她穿着红色礼服登上舞台，就像一位休闲歌手，在爵士乐队和舞者的伴奏下，表演了<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/artist/drake/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/artist/drake/"  >Drake 的</a>特色歌曲“ <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/drake-sexyy-red-bbl-drizzy-new-precedent-ai-sample-clearances/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/pro/drake-sexyy-red-bbl-drizzy-new-precedent-ai-sample-clearances/"  >U My Everything</a> ”。 </p><div class="injected-related-story // lrv-u-margin-tb-2 lrv-u-border-t-1 lrv-u-border-b-1 lrv-u-padding-t-050 lrv-u-padding-b-075 lrv-u-border-color-grey" ><div class="a-heading-border a-heading-border-background-color-grey a-heading-border-height-075 lrv-u-margin-b-075 lrv-u-margin-b-050@mobile-max"><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  lrv-u-color-brand-primary a-font-primary-bold-s lrv-u-text-transform-uppercase lrv-u-padding-r-1 a-article-related-module-title a-article-related-module-title--color-brand-primary">有关的</h3></div><div class="o-card lrv-u-flex"><div class="c-lazy-image  lrv-u-height-100p"><div class="a-crop-3x2 a-crop-1x1@mobile-max lrv-u-height-100p"><img decoding="async" class="c-lazy-image__img lrv-u-background-color-grey-lightest lrv-u-width-100p lrv-u-display-block lrv-u-height-auto" src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/themes/vip/pmc-billboard-2021/assets/public/lazyload-fallback.gif" data-lazy-src="https://www.billboard.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Usher-03-award-bet-awards-show-2024-billboard-1548.jpg?w=237&#038;h=147&#038;crop=1" alt="招待员" data-lazy-srcset="" data-lazy-sizes="" height="" width=""></div></div></div><div class="o-card__content lrv-u-flex lrv-u-flex-direction-column lrv-u-justify-content-center lrv-u-padding-lr-1 lrv-u-padding-lr-075@mobile-max"><div class="o_category "></div><div class="c_title "><h3 id="title-of-a-story" class="c-title  a-font-primary-medium-m lrv-u-padding-b-050 u-letter-spacing-0028@mobile-max"> 2024 年 BET 奖获奖者：查看完整列表（更新中） </h3></div><time class="c-timestamp  a-font-primary-medium-xxs lrv-u-color-brand-primary lrv-u-order-100" datetime="00:00-YY-DD-MM"> 2024/06/30 </time></div></div></div><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>然后，她完全改变了氛围，在类似白宫的台阶上表演了她的热门歌曲“ <a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/sexyy-red-get-it-sexyy-top-10-hot-rb-hip-hop-songs-chart-1235654108/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/sexyy-red-get-it-sexyy-top-10-hot-rb-hip-hop-songs-chart-1235654108/"  >Get It sexyy</a> ”。当她穿着白衬衫和细条纹裙子扭臀时，人群变得疯狂。你没看错：她最新的磁带<em><a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/sexyy-red-in-sexyy-we-trust-ep-listen-1235692070/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/sexyy-red-in-sexyy-we-trust-ep-listen-1235692070/"  >《性感我们信任》</a></em>充分诠释了总统主题。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>她将在<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/sexyy-red-4-president-tour-dates-2024-1235717307/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/sexyy-red-4-president-tour-dates-2024-1235717307/"  >最近宣布的</a>“Sexyy Red 4 President”美国巡演中进行巡演，该巡演将于 8 月在西雅图拉开帷幕。她计划在 26 个城市进行演出，最后一场演出是 10 月 1 日在纳什维尔，她将于 9 月 13 日在家乡圣路易斯进行现场表演。Hunxho、Loe Shimmy 和圣路易斯人 BlakeIANA 将在揭幕战。门票已经开始发售，您可以<a  rel="nofollow"  href="https://sexyy4president.com/pages/tour"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://sexyy4president.com/pages/tour"  target="_blank"  >在这里</a>找到。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
> sexyy 也将目光投向了全球统治地位，她将在无线音乐节、罗斯基勒音乐节和 Rolling Loud Europe 音乐节上亮相，然后返回美国进行正式竞选活动。</p><p
		class="paragraph larva // lrv-u-margin-lr-auto  lrv-a-font-body-m   "
>她演唱的两首歌曲均在<a  href="https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/"  data-type="link"  data-id="https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/"  >Billboard Hot 100</a>排行榜上保持强势，其中由 Drake 演唱的《Get It sexyy》和《U My Everything》分别排名第 38 名和第 59 名。</p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 1235721235</post-id></item><item><title>安德拉·戴 (Andra Day) 畅谈大二专辑《CASSANDRA》、为何花了这么长时间才发行以及更多内容 | 2024 年BET 奖</title><link/>https://www.billboard.com/video/andra-day-chats-sophomore-album-cassandra-why-it-took-so-long-to-release-it-more-bet-awards-2024/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Katie Cao]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Mon, 01 Jul 2024 01:47:11 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Videos]]></category><category><![CDATA[BET Awards 2024]]></category><category><![CDATA[Billboard]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.billboard.com/?post_type=pmc_top_video&amp;p=1235721297 </guid><description><![CDATA[Andra Day chatted with Billboard’s Carl Lamarre on the red carpet of the 2024 BET Awards.]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- do not apply CSS styles to this element! --><div class="pmc-not-a-paywall"><p
